name.jp: 可愛いマトリョーシカ

description.en: Typically, Babushka dolls (Or Matroyshka Dolls) consist of a set of finely crafted wooden dolls placed inside of each other. You might say, they're full of themselves!
description.ar: Typically, Babushka dolls (Or Matroyshka Dolls) consist of a set of finely crafted wooden dolls placed inside of each other. You might say, they're full of themselves!
description.br: Normalmente, as bonecas Russas (ou bonecas Matrioscas) consistem em um conjunto de bonecas de madeira finamente confeccionadas, colocadas umas dentro das outras. Você pode dizer que elas estão cheias de si!
description.cns: 通常情况下，套娃由一组精心制作的木偶组成，这些木偶彼此放置在一起。你可能会说，他们充满了自己！
description.de: Eine russische Puppe, die dir überall hin folgt und deine Items einsammelt.

description.fr: Une poupée russe aux joues rouges qui suit son maître et ramasse les objets laissés par les monstres.
description.id: Biasanya, boneka Babushka (Atau Boneka Matroyshka) terdiri dari satu set boneka kayu yang dibuat dengan baik yang ditempatkan di dalam satu sama lain. Mungkin bisa dikatakan, mereka penuh dengan diri mereka sendiri!
description.it: Typically, Babushka dolls (Or Matroyshka Dolls) consist of a set of finely crafted wooden dolls placed inside of each other. You might say, they're full of themselves!
description.jp: 通常、バブーシュカ人形（またはマトリョーシカ人形）は、互いに内側に配置された細かく細工された木製の人形のセットで構成されています。あなたは言うかもしれません、彼らは彼ら自身でいっぱいです！
description.kr: 일반적으로 바부시카 인형 (또는 마트로시카)은 정교하게 만들어진 나무 인형 세트로 구성되어 있습니다. 당신은 그들 자신으로 가득 차 있다고 말할 수 있습니다!

description.th: โดยทั่วไปแล้ว Babushka dolls(หรือ Matroyshka Dolls) จะประกอบด้วยชุดตุ๊กตาไม้ที่ประดิษฐ์ขึ้นอย่างประณีตที่วางอยู่ภายในกันและกัน บอกเลยว่าจัดเต็ม!
description.tw: 召喚或解除可愛的俄羅斯娃娃。
description.vi: Điển hình là búp bê Babushka (Hay Búp bê Matroyshka) bao gồm một bộ búp bê bằng gỗ được chế tác tinh xảo đặt bên trong nhau. Bạn có thể nói, chúng đầy bản thân!
